'''小約翰·理查德·卡西奇'''（{{lang-en|John Richard Kasich Jr.}}，{{bd|1952年|5月13日}}<ref name="westervillelibrary.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.westervillelibrary.org/kasich/bio/ |title=Biography | John R. Kasich Congressional Collection |publisher=Westervillelibrary.org |date=1952-05-15 |accessdate=2013-07-19 |archive-date=2013-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131017031302/http://www.westervillelibrary.org/kasich/bio/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>），曾任[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]]第69任{{tsl|en|List of Governors of Ohio|俄亥俄州州長|州長}}。2010年首任，並於2014年連任<ref name=governor>{{cite news|work=Governor of Ohio|title=Governor John R. Kasich Biography|url=http://www.governor.ohio.gov/About/GovernorKasich.aspx|access-date=2016-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729233008/http://governor.ohio.gov/About/GovernorKasich.aspx|archive-date=2017-07-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2015年7月21日，卡西奇宣布有意代表共和黨角逐[[2016年美國總統選舉|2016年美國總統]]候選人提名<ref name="catch-up">{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/22/us/politics/john-kasich-election-2016-presidential-race.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=photo-spot-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0 | title=John Kasich Enters Crowded 2016 Race Facing Job of Catch-Up | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=July 21, 2015 | accessdate=July 21, 2015 | author=Stolberg, Sheryl Gay | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304095014/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/07/22/us/politics/john-kasich-election-2016-presidential-race.html?hp&action=click&pgtype=Homepage&module=photo-spot-region&region=top-news&WT.nav=top-news&_r=0 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Easley, Jonathan. [http://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/249984-kasich-wastes-no-time-moving-up-in-the-polls Kasich makes quick rise in polls] {{Wayback|url=http://thehill.com/homenews/campaign/249984-kasich-wastes-no-time-moving-up-in-the-polls |date=20160210105047 }}, ''[[The_Hill_(newspaper)|The Hill]]'' (August 2, 2015): "in the two weeks since he launched his presidential campaign, John Kasich has bypassed New Jersey Gov. Chris Christie, former Texas Gov. Rick Perry and other Republicans who have been in the race longer."</ref>。

卡西奇曾任九屆[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]議員，為{{tsl|en|Ohio's 12th congressional district|俄亥俄州第十二选区}}代表，任期由1983年至2001年止<ref name=congress>{{cite news|work=Biographical Directory of the United States Congress|url=http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=K000016|title=KASICH, John Richard, Biographical Information|accessdate=2016-02-10|archive-date=2012-07-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69BSvJZBt?url=http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=K000016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在眾議員任內，卡西奇擔任了18年的[[美国众议院军事委员会|軍事委員會]]委員，以及6年的{{tsl|en|United States House Committee on the Budget|美国众院预算委员会|預算委員會}}主席。他是推動{{tsl|en|Personal Responsibility and Work Opportunity Act|个人责任与工作机会法案|福利改革}}與{{tsl|en|Balanced Budget Act of 1997|1997年平衡预算法案}}等法案的重要人物。

2001年至2007年間，卡西奇曾在[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]擔任評論員，並主持過《{{tsl|en|Heartland with John Kasich|凱西克的心脏地带}}》節目。他亦曾為{{tsl|en|Investment banking|投资银行业务|投资银行家}}、[[雷曼兄弟|雷曼兄弟]]位於俄亥俄州[[哥伦布_(俄亥俄州)|哥倫布]]辦公室的[[首席执行官|董事总经理]]<ref name="lehman-race">{{cite news | url = http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/2010-election-wall-street-factor-ohio-governors-race/story?id=10586618 | publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]] | accessdate = 2012-09-05 | first = Teddy | last = Davis | title = Lehman Brothers Collapse Haunts John Kasich in Ohio Governor's Race | date = May 12, 2010 | archive-date = 2012-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103081800/http://abcnews.go.com/Politics/2010-election-wall-street-factor-ohio-governors-race/story?id=10586618 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="dayton-daily-news">{{cite news | work = Dayton Daily News | url = http://www.daytondailynews.com/blogs/content/shared-gen/blogs/dayton/ohiopolitics/entries/2010/04/02/kasich_made_11_m_in_2008_no_go.html/ | title = Kasich made $1.1 M in 2008; no "golden parachute" from Lehman Bros, records show | first = William | last = Hershey | accessdate = 2012-09-05 | date = April 2, 2010 | archive-date = 2012-01-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120125230412/http://www.daytondailynews.com/blogs/content/shared-gen/blogs/dayton/ohiopolitics/entries/2010/04/02/kasich_made_11_m_in_2008_no_go.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在競選俄亥俄州州長的選舉中，卡西奇擊敗了[[民主党_(美国)|民主黨]]現任州長[[泰德·史垂克蘭德|史垂克蘭]]<ref name=election>{{cite news|work=Ohio Secretary of State|title=Governor and Lieutenant Governor: November 2, 2010|url=https://www.sos.state.oh.us/sos/elections/Research/electResultsMain/2010results/20101102governor.aspx|accessdate=2016-02-10|archive-date=2016-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160210055942/http://www.sos.state.oh.us/sos/elections/Research/electResultsMain/2010results/20101102governor.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年爭取連任時，以壓倒性優勢擊敗民主黨對手{{tsl|en|Ed FitzGerald|艾德·費茲傑羅|費茲傑羅}}。

2015年7月，卡西奇宣布將競選[[2016年美國總統選舉|美國總統]]。

